## Write a program to find area of a cube

Area of cube = 6 × `Side`^2

```txt
Side : 2

Area : 24
```

---

<CodeBlock slug="find-area-of-a-cube" >

```c
#include<stdio.h>

int main(){
    int side;
    scanf("%d",&side);
    int area=6*side*side;
    printf("Area of the cube: %d",area);
    return 0;
}
```

